{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3672e29944","title":"谢富治接见北京红卫兵代表的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"19948a0105","index":0,"year":1967,"month":2,"day":6,"articleId":"3672e29944","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"大联合","id":"18bf6a78fe","type":"主题"},{"name":"对话","id":"314ad57c4d","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"红卫兵运动","id":"3be4d5766f","type":"主题"},{"name":"暴力和武斗","id":"3bff1d2fc6","type":"主题"},{"name":"谢富治","id":"93cca4665d","type":"人物"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"85b13f5c0b","name":"谢富治"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ac0f4f486f","type":"title","text":"谢富治接见北京红卫兵代表的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3672e29944","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ccc467a4fe","type":"paragraph","text":"〖被接见者：北京红卫兵三个司令部代表及其他人员〗","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3672e29944","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"005f1e60c8","type":"paragraph","text":"一、支持成立首都革命造反红卫兵代表大会，但这个名词不太好，建议换一下。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3672e29944","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d4d68e87e1","type":"paragraph","text":"二、赞成一个学校派一个组织。暂时不收中学生。在中学生中，目前左派队伍还比较混乱。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3672e29944","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c49f90b9ae","type":"paragraph","text":"三、建议学生帮助首都三个工人造反组织进行整顿，并联合起来。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3672e29944","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c0532fedd8","type":"paragraph","text":"四、目前学生组织中你吞并我，我吞并你是不对的，应该联合，左派之间发生了很多矛盾，出现了武斗现象，这是不符合主席的坚持文斗，不要武斗。如发生了类似现象，应遵守以下三条：","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3672e29944","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8bd2c8d6a7","type":"paragraph","text":"第一，不能打架，","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3672e29944","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"53f7756777","type":"paragraph","text":"第二，不能撒传单，贴大字报，","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3672e29944","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"12dbb58324","type":"paragraph","text":"第三，不要开动宣传车互相攻击，有缺点和错误应在内部讨论。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3672e29944","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}